sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client
    participant Orch as Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>8033/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Chunker as Chunker Service<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant Detector as Detector Service(s)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant TGIS as TGIS Generation<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant NLP as caikit-nlp<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant OpenAI as OpenAI-compatible<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS

    Note over Client,OpenAI: Flow 1: Text Content Detection (Unary)
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/text/detection/content<br/>TLS (optional), Header passthrough
    Orch->>Chunker: ChunkerTokenizationTaskPredict<br/>gRPC, TLS/mTLS (configurable)
    Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked text segments
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Header passthrough
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results
    Orch-->>Client: Aggregated detection response

    Note over Client,OpenAI: Flow 2: Classification with Text Generation (Streaming)
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v1/task/server-streaming-classification-with-text-generation<br/>TLS (optional), Header passthrough
    Orch->>TGIS: GenerateStream<br/>gRPC, TLS/mTLS (configurable)
    TGIS-->>Orch: Generated text stream
    Orch->>Chunker: ChunkerTokenizationTaskPredict<br/>gRPC, TLS/mTLS (configurable)
    Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked segments
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/generation<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Header passthrough
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results
    Orch-->>Client: SSE stream with classified results

    Note over Client,OpenAI: Flow 3: OpenAI Chat Completions with Detection
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>TLS (optional), Header passthrough
    Orch->>OpenAI: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Bearer token (API key)
    OpenAI-->>Orch: Chat completion response
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Header passthrough
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results
    Orch-->>Client: JSON or SSE stream response
